{"word":"G5459 - φωσφόρος - phōsphóros - foce-for'-os - Day star","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φωσφόρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phōsphóros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">foce-for'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Day star</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"விடிவெள்ளியான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"light - bringing, giving light"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5457 - φῶς - phōs - foce/5457\">G5457</a> and <a href=\"#/G5342 - φέρω - phérō - fer'-o/5342\">G5342</a>; <i>light bearing</i> (&ldquo;phosphorus&rdquo;), that is, (specifically) the <i>morning star</i> (figuratively): - day star.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2017/2017\">G2017</a>, <a href=\"#/G2020/2020\">G2020</a>, <a href=\"#/G5457/5457\">G5457</a>, <a href=\"#/G5458/5458\">G5458</a>, <a href=\"#/G5459/5459\">G5459</a>, <a href=\"#/G5460/5460\">G5460</a>, <a href=\"#/G5461/5461\">G5461</a>, <a href=\"#/G5462/5462\">G5462</a>"}]}